originalText.text:
My children took TKD at this facility around 8 to 9 years ago. They also enjoyed the summer camp offer by Warriors TKD. It was one of the best decisions I’ve ever made, as it was an amazing experience for them, one that they still hold and embrace. And, I was certain that I was leaving my children in a safe place with a healthy environment.

Today I’m back with my younger boy and he is having a blast. Warriors TKD have great masters and instructors. The best ones, in my opinion…
